# Shared Agent Guidance

`AGENTS.md` is the repo entry point and `.agents/shared-instructions.md` is the shared instruction source for this repository.

- Read and follow `AGENTS.md`, then `.agents/shared-instructions.md`, before applying tool-specific preferences.
- Treat `.agents/shared-instructions.md` as the common source of truth across Cursor, Claude, and similar coding agents.
- Keep `AGENTS.md` as the root auto-load pointer and keep the substantive shared guidance in the hidden `.agents/` folder.
